      "description": "This car is in fair condition. It runs and drives but has some mechanical issues that may need attention in the near term. The interior shows moderate wear including some staining and minor damage to the upholstery. The exterior has visible scratches and a few small dents. Overall a functional vehicle that will require some work.",
